strings.Value: "As we walk in light, we shall not forget those lost in darkness."
"I pray for peace, and an easy path for the fallen."
"Speak slowly, I'm writing it down. I shall cite your prayers in my essay on the cult of Sarenrae."
"Let us remember the fallen with dignity! Our sorrow, and our pride in them, shall live on in our hearts."
"Your words heap sadness upon my soul, but relieve it as well."
"They stopped caring about your sermons long ago. Just like everyone else."
